r side, facing inward toward the table. The room is airy and bright, with tall windows, open shelves, counters, and kitchen items arranged neatly in the background. White on-screen text near the bottom reads, “Thank goodness for male bonding,” matching the visual joke of the man and the children sharing a messy mealtime moment.",
